-#
  Presents a confirmation message before attempting to remove a user from a club

  Expects the following instance variavles to be defined

  @param [userClub] user_club The relationship that will be destroyed
#removeUser
  .modal-header
    %h2.modal-title= t('user_club.destroy')
  .modal-body
    = form_tag club_admin_path(@user_club), method: :delete do
      .form-horizontal
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-12= t('user_club.confirm_remove', user_name: @user_club.user_name)
          = render 'public/modal_form_buttons'
